## Limitations

The analysis is based on available data up to October 2023, and some sources may have been published after this date, potentially affecting the timeliness of the information. Additionally, the report relies on secondary data from various sources, which may introduce bias or incomplete perspectives. Further research, including primary data collection and expert interviews, could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the motivations behind the promotion of Medicare Advantage plans.

